            "summary": "sketch This is a just a fun character concept that gave interesting&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01071_.png\" data-size=\"944x1128\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01071_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"918\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/scan0012.jpg\" data-size=\"1579x1890\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/scan0012-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"919\"></a>\n<figcaption>sketch</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01070_.png\" data-size=\"944x1128\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01070_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"918\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01069_.png\" data-size=\"944x1128\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01069_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"918\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01055_.png\" data-size=\"944x1128\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01055_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"918\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01053_.png\" data-size=\"944x1128\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/43/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01053_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"918\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a just a fun character concept that gave interesting information about color and patterns interpretations by AI. I found these results enlightening about how AI chooses color patterns and designs based on colors and design structure of the image.</p>",
