        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/figgy-apple-newton.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/figgy-apple-newton.html",
            "title": "Figgy Apple Newton",
            "summary": "The fun thing about letting imagination steer a concept, you never know&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/42/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01051_.png\" data-size=\"1264x936\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/42/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01051_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"569\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/42/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01050_.png\" data-size=\"1264x936\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/42/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01050_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"569\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/42/gallery/scan0006-2.jpg\" data-size=\"2110x1570\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/42/gallery/scan0006-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"571\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>The fun thing about letting imagination steer a concept, you never know where it will go. What things it will combine to tell a story. Whenever I create and stop and walk away, and come back and look at what I made, it is always a gift. The more info you give to AI the more interesting the final picture can become. It was fun to give this colored pencil image a touch of realism.</p>",
