        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/david-and-goliath.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/david-and-goliath.html",
            "title": "David and Goliath",
            "summary": "A surreal interpretation of a very old story of overcoming impossible odds.",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01573_.png\" data-size=\"1936x2592\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01573_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/IMG_20131211_081137.jpg\" data-size=\"1936x2592\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/IMG_20131211_081137-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01574_.png\" data-size=\"1936x2592\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01574_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01575_.png\" data-size=\"1936x2592\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01575_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01577_.png\" data-size=\"1936x2592\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01577_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01578_.png\" data-size=\"1936x2592\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01578_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01579_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1552\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/39/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01579_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>A surreal interpretation of a very old story of overcoming impossible odds. The AI outputs surprised me that it pretty much got the concept of the two facing off, however it lacked the ability to to the building along the path, I got creative with the prompt to make a finished image in one take.</p>",
