        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/collage-of-my-artwork.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/collage-of-my-artwork.html",
            "title": "Collage of my Artwork",
            "summary": "Photoshop This was one of my first digital art pieces in Photoshop&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01088_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01088_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01087_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01087_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01086_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01086_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01085_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01085_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/smallcollage.jpg\" data-size=\"600x600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/38/gallery/smallcollage-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"></a>\n<figcaption>Photoshop</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This was one of my first digital art pieces in Photoshop taking different pieces from different works of art i created and making a collage, learning about Photoshop and creating art : ). I was very interested to see how all of this together was interpreted by AI. It is interesting how certain shapes are always percieved the same by AI.</p>",
