            "summary": "Just a fun sketch of a character, an odd bug guy that&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01305_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01305_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/scan0011.jpg\" data-size=\"954x1937\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/scan0011-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1559\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01304_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01304_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01324_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01324_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01332_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01332_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01338_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/36/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01338_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>Just a fun sketch of a character, an odd bug guy that everytime I see him I think he is standing outside a club. So given how I always see him, I had to use AI and put him outside a club surrounded by people trying to get into the club. </p>",
