            "summary": "This rough sketch is inspired by what mediation can do for the&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/35/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01076_.png\" data-size=\"1400x992\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/35/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01076_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"544\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/35/gallery/IMG_20131211_101622-trimmed.jpg\" data-size=\"2341x1663\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/35/gallery/IMG_20131211_101622-trimmed-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"546\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This rough sketch is inspired by what mediation can do for the human mind. When you take some time for yourself and forget the worries of the day. The concept of the image is taken from the pendulum that swings in a grandfather clock. The AI is still a work in progress, but the imagery AI create from the sketch is still pretty : )</p>",
